1:1 COMMENT "# unit_dissect_value.z -- compile-time dissection of a generic UNIT's NUMERIC"
1:78 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "# value parameter. `match cap` inside a `unit as { cap: u32.generic }` selects"
2:79 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# an arm by the parameter's concrete VALUE at monomorphisation; only the"
3:73 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# matching arm survives in the generated C (the #ifdef analogue over a"
4:71 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# compile-time constant), just like the value form on classes."
5:63 EOL "\n"
